‚ÄúWonderful. Great earthy ( Organic ) taste with a heavy stone that's immediate. This strain reminds me of the first  times I really enjoyed the high. I don't normally write about the pain qualities in a strain either because we all know ...‚Äù

‚ÄúCinex

Smell: VERY earthy, almost spicy

Taste: definitely spicy, with a pungent background to it

Probability of munchies: medium

Effects: very euphoric and uplifting mentally, and very light and tingly on the body. This strain is a hit or miss with anxiety, I find it borders on the too up-itty" feeling that can set off panic attacks in some
